{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-194-coloured-configurations","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 194: Raspored boja","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Zamislite crteže napravljene sa jedinicama A: <img alt=\"graph unit A\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/coloured-configurations-1.png\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: white; padding: 10px;\"> i B: <img  alt=\"graph unit B\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/coloured-configurations-2.png\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: white; padding: 10px;\">, gde su jedinice povezane duž vertikalne ivice kao što je prikazano na crtežu <img alt=\"graph with four units glued along the vertical edges\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/coloured-configurations-3.png\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: white; padding: 10px;\">.</p>\n<p>Raspored tipa $(a,b,c)$ je figura napravljena na $a$ jedinica A i $b$ jedinica B, gde su vrhovi figure obojeni korišćenjem boja do $c$, na način da dva dodirujuća vršnja ne dele istu boju. Prikazani mešoviti crtež je primer rasporeda tipa $(2,2,6)$, posebno tipa $(2,2,c)$ za svako $c \\geq 4$.</p>\n<p>Neka $N(a,b,c)$ bude broj aranžmana tipa $(a,b,c)$. Na primer, $N(1,0,3) = 24$, $N(0,2,4) = 92928$ i $N(2,2,3) = 20736$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi poslednjih 8 cifara za $N(25,75,1984)$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f42f1000cf542c50ff40","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301832,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-194-coloured-configurations"},"required":[],"usesMultifil